Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to be followed by any re-submission activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' cases until 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Minimum time for a declaration to be 'REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and then 'FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' before being approved or finalized
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Time to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' since the initial submission by employee
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to be resolved or escalated within the process flow
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to be followed by a final decision (approval or rejection)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case
